description: On tonight's episode, we discuss the rumor of a divided Winnipeg Jets locker-room involving Mark Scheifele and Blake Wheeler. Does this all mean Scheifele will leave Winnipeg over the summer, or can the situation be salvaged? We then discuss the current NHL playoff series, including the chaotic match-up between the Toronto Maple Leafs and Tampa Bay Lightning. Were the Leafs able to close out business, or will they now have to win game 7 on home ice? How did the Minnesota Wild end up exiting in the first round?
